name: 9to5
description: The "9-5" token is designed to encapsulate the essence of breaking free from the conventional 9-to-5 work paradigm. Launched with a visionary approach, 9-5 represents more than just a cryptocurrency; it symbolizes a movement towards financial independence and personal freedom, challenging the traditional notion of working a standard job to make a living. Not only does it represent financial freedom but also a ticket to a community that believes in living life on their own terms.
